Package flounder.space

Contains classes useful for representing and manipulating multidimensional flounder.space.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISpatialObject
    Represents an object that has some notion of flounder.space, and can be stored in a ISpatialStructure.
    ISpatialStructure<T extends ISpatialObject>
    A data structure that stores objects with a notion of flounder.space.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Frustum
    Represents the region of flounder.space in the modeled world that may appear on the screen.
    StructureBasic<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 3D space.
    StructureGrid<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 2D space with a grid.
    StructureOctree<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 3D space that can be recursively divided into 8 equal subspaces.
    StructureQuadtree<T extends ISpatialObject>
    Represents a 2D space that can be recursively divided into 4 equal subspaces.
